{"tid":1358710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"21/7 貨VAN司機片段","createTime":"2019-07-24T03:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T13:40:22.000Z","uid":48379,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"920fc0641eaa972b577a5c8aed6207c169d8e61a","tid":1358710,"uid":48379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wqb117f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwqb117f.jpg&h=4b168336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開頭冇拍到，我用文字講，<br />\n一開始有好多車駛過嚟，架貨VAN同7人車係頭車，後面有幾多車就睇唔到，<br />\n啲車見到有路障就開始停，停左係point A(見圖)，<br />\n貨VAN司機有落車，我地亦都有幾個示威者上前同佢地講前面封左路，<br />\n傾左around幾十秒，貨VAN司機上返車，開車，諗住用架衝車衝出去(見圖白色箭咀)，<br />\n所以大家見到點解架淨係得架貨VAN係前面，<br />\n有個勇士但係前面同身體擋(point B)，貨VAN司機都有停車，然後就落車(開始video片段)<br />\n<br />\nvideo片段中間都有好多人討論緊睇下點樣安排佢地(車)點樣走，<br />\n後面慢慢後退定係開路唔知點，未討論完個VAN司機就爆seed<br />\n<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1Gjd7_Q0Dxx8ziRsYbwQAMgvgNqbL9P5M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1Gjd7_Q0Dxx8ziRsYbwQAMgvgNqbL9P5M&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=d5cd3b66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1Gjd7_Q0Dxx8ziRsYbwQAMgvgNqbL9P5M</a><br />\n<br />\ncut短咗：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1EIUZXPI3CZq1dcOpVjgvppG9ZEbbpGON\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1EIUZXPI3CZq1dcOpVjgvppG9ZEbbpGON&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=8f08c3dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1EIUZXPI3CZq1dcOpVjgvppG9ZEbbpGON</a>"},{"pid":"2483edc65e69386871755d92a84832d11e6f26bb","tid":1358710,"uid":48379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"920fc0641eaa972b577a5c8aed6207c169d8e61a","tid":1358710,"uid":48379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wqb117f.jpg\" da